Status report of Yi Tong Tse on 8/24/98

Developed a generalized, frame-accurate splicing algorithm which can handle
switching from one channel to another.  This general algorithm can handle,
with reduced complexity, the special case of ad insertion where the ad
is a pre-coded bitstream with pre-conditioned entry and exit points.
Converted the algorithms into a set of claims which have been added to
the seamless splicing patent description.

Finished a set of routines to read and write MPEG-2 video bitstreams.

